# UX & Accessibility Guardrails

## Design System
- 4px baseline spacing (4px, 8px, 12px, 16px, 20px, 24px)
- Tailwind CSS v4 utility classes
- Mobile-first responsive design

## States
- Every screen must have loading/empty/error/success states

## Accessibility
- WCAG 2.2 AA baseline required
- Semantic HTML first, ARIA only if needed
- All interactive elements keyboard accessible
- Color contrast meets WCAG 2.2 AA (4.5:1 text, 3:1 UI)
- All images have descriptive alt attributes
